; UNSAT: (x * x + 1) == 0 for 12-bit x
; No solution: x^2+1 is never 0 mod 2^12 (since -1 is not a quadratic residue mod powers of 2 for n>=3)
; Forces exhaustive search over 4096 values
; Expected: UNSAT
1 sort bitvec 12
2 sort bitvec 1
3 input 1 x
4 mul 1 3 3
5 one 1
6 add 1 4 5
7 zero 1
8 eq 2 6 7
9 bad 8
